craterdog.collections.interfaces

Interface Ordered<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of element managed by the collection.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Composite, java.lang.Iterable<E>, Iteratable<E>, Sequential<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bag, OrderedCollection, Set

    public interface Ordered<E>
extends Iteratable<E>
    This interface defines the methods that must be implemented by each collection that supports an implicit ordering of its elements.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
